{
  "stem": "13851.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one of the guys from my hometown, he had made a fire, and we put down on the brick the few potatoes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I look in the front, and the head of the SS in the front of me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So what I did-- I-- he was so tall, I run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I ran through his feet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I [? did ?] run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't run no place else, but I got so scared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what happened in the evening, the appell, they called-- if anything happened, they had an appell.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I told you what appell is, standing all from the camps in lines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I told you I had a number, 167.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they called-- called up, and I thought they're going to take me into the woods to be killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But the head of the-- I remember his name was Nel, N-E-L.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was the head of-- head of SS in Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said I should get 24 on my back, 24 lashes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they-- and we had in our-- it was--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and that was-- if not that, I would have to-- usually, that something that happened, that somebody gave him the idea of telling this to do to me.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because mostly when something bad happen, they took the people out to be killed in the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I had to lay down on a chair, and there were the head of the Jewish policeman in that Blizyn.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One from one side and other side, and I got 25 on my rear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then after that happened, I was bleeding like from my tush, that-- that he's like, you putting potatoes in the ground was like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was laying down in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was crying, screaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was what happened at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
